| W7 | PR #9 | 30 approved trace specs + 4 role suites scoring |
| W8 | PR #10 (B) | Deterministic tools reduce TB 2.0 cost ≥ 20 % |
| W9 | PR #10 (C–D) | Planner + multi-agent fan-out live; TB 2.0 wall time −30 % on multi-read tasks |
| W10 | PR #10 (E) | Strong re-entry live; recovery rate measured |
